# Security & production safety

## Secrets
- Never commit secrets (API keys, tokens, passwords, private URLs, customer data).
- If you see a likely secret in diff/context: call it out and remove/redact it.

## Production
- Treat production as **read-only** unless explicitly authorized.
- If a request implies production changes, stop and ask for explicit approval + rollout plan.
